# applypilot.ai

Core domain models for tracking job applications.

## Setup

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
python -m pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Run tests

```bash
pytest
```

## Usage example

```python
from datetime import date
from applypilot import ApplicationStatus, JobApplication

app = JobApplication(
    company="OpenAI",
    role="Software Engineer",
    source="Careers page",
    applied_on=date.today(),
)

app.transition_to(ApplicationStatus.APPLIED)
app.transition_to(ApplicationStatus.INTERVIEW)
app.transition_to(ApplicationStatus.OFFER)
```
